title: Week 10 Preview: Chris Wesseling is back, plus ATN's first 'lock off'
itunes:title: Week 10 Preview: Chris Wesseling is back, plus ATN's first 'lock off'
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Gregg Rosenthal & Chris Wesseling take a look at all of the Week 10 action, starting with a recap of Thursday night’s Seahawks-Cardinals showdown (1:00), which included a contender for Call of the Year (6:10); Dan shows off his superb singing voice by belting out his lock of the week, just before Marc calls for a LOCK OFF (22:00); Why no one feels bad for the struggling Packers without Aaron Rodgers (25:00); (26:00) Wess talks about one player on his radar and compares him to Eddie Haskell (45:30); Plus much more!
